metadata.description: **Join the movement here:** ***https://kongz.art.*** *First time offered: AI-generated Genesis and Baby CyberKongz oil masterpieces.* CyberKongz stands among the most highly valued and coveted NFT collections.  The ten “legendary” Kongz command millions of dollars on the rare occasion when they are sold.  Even “floor” CyberKongz sell for well over $500,000 dollars. For the first time, you can mint AI-generated oil renderings of the full CyberKongz Genesis and Baby collection.  This incredibly detailed and gorgeous collection uses over 100 AI technologies and includes all ten Legendary Kongz as well as the 910 “OG” Kongz and Baby Kongz.  Mint before they’re gone, and experience CyberKongz like never before!  Sell, trade, collect, or use however you would like during this era of explosive metaverse growth. Only one minting is available for each of the 4,000 CyberKongz, with each owner receiving an individual ERC-721 token with proof of ownership on the Ethereum blockchain.
